    "body" : "<p>subclass the dialect</p>\n\n<p>and</p>\n\n<pre><code>registerFunction(\"group_concat\", new StandardSQLFunction(\"group_concat\", Hibernate.STRING));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or use <a href=\"http://elliottjorgensen.com/nhibernate-api-ref/NHibernate.Dialect.Function/SQLFunctionTemplate.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">SQLFunctionTemplate</a></p>\n"
  }, {
