      "body" : "<code>Hibernate.STRING</code> has been deprecated since Hibernate version 3.6.X <a href=\"https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/orm/3.6/javadocs/org/hibernate/Hibernate.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Here is the deprecated document</a>, so you have to use <code>StringType.INSTANCE</code>."
