    "body" : "<p>If you are using createSQLQuery, use addScalar to that column as String.</p>\n\n<pre><code>SQLQuery query = sessionObj.createSQLQuery(\"select group_concat(column1,column2) as mycolumn from some table group by someThing\");\nquery.addScalar(\"mycolumn \", Hibernate.STRING);\n</code></pre>\n"
