    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Instead of <code>Group_concat</code> you could use hibernate's function of</p>\n<p><code>ARRAY_AGG(column1) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY column1)</code></p>\n"
